{"tid":1282973,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"住警察宿舍嘅手足入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-03T16:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T16:43:06.000Z","uid":2798,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7c146c1cdab8bb38ece8d37f028cf88bbbe654dc","tid":1282973,"uid":2798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:40:21.000Z","msg":"大家或者有屋企人係黑警<br />\n但又無自立能力，屋企人唔俾你去發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過唔緊要，就做個守法市民！<br />\n我聽我朋友講好多住警察宿舍偷偷地養狗<br />\n朋友話成日聽到有狗吠聲，好嘈<br />\n咁唔守規矩，我定一定要投訴！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDky7kW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDky7kW.png&h=2295ac30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警告你送走隻家蓄，唔肯送唔知會唔會無咗宿舍呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔守規矩嘅宿舍黑警快啲同自己隻狗講定拜拜啦<br />\n<br />\nPs:我住柴灣翠灣邨附近，有無人覺得樓下合作舍餐廳好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dfc49098e9d639675f16b04fd33251eb8521a2","tid":1282973,"uid":185184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:41:00.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"ebf3d99fd43d56bdb0000f0f0d3043a232eff3e6","tid":1282973,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"我有FD已經搬左出黎"},{"pid":"ccb903f102d62b22dec87aa84a37915d29909e7b","tid":1282973,"uid":2798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ebf3d99fd43d56bdb0000f0f0d3043a232eff3e6","tid":1282973,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"我有FD已經搬左出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"返去掃樓撐警加探父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}